 Vehicle License Automation

## Overview
A Python-based application designed to automate parts of the vehicle licensing process, including form completion and document generation.

---

## Features
- Streamlit-based user interface
- Automated PDF generation
- Document handling and form workflows
- Data input and processing

---

## Tech Stack
- Python
- Streamlit
- PyPDF
- ReportLab
- python-docx

---

## What This Project Demonstrates
- Building real-world automation tools
- Working with document generation
- Backend logic and workflows
- Problem-solving in admin-heavy processes
